<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮子大吼一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮子扑向普斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯奔跑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狮子就是食人魔！” 他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯冲进了一个走廊里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么才能逃出城堡呢？” 他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯跑过拐角，看到楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮子张开大嘴咬了一口。嘎吱！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！” 普斯跑上楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯跑进一个小房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快速跑到窗外躲起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮子闻了闻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到你了，猫！” 狮子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>窗外露出了狮子的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这儿！” 狮子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！” 普斯说，“你很擅长变身。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮子点点头。“是的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以变成任何东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我猜你不能变得更大了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我当然能！” 狮子大喊，“看我的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮子很快就变大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！他的头撞到了窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！” 狮子往后倒了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯往房间里偷看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮子又变回了食人魔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很痛苦地摸着自己的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是逃跑的机会！” 普斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄从窗户溜进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地从食人魔身边走过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快到门口了……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只大手抓住了普斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔大笑。“抓到你了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
